---
import Section from "~/layouts/Section.astro";
import Layout from "~/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Publication from "~/widgets/Publication.astro";
import Design from "~/widgets/Design.astro";
---

<Layout title="About" id="about">
  <main>
    <div class="h-3"></div>

    <h1 class="md:max-w-[800px] mx-auto">
      <div
        class="flex max-sm:flex-col gap-2 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-2xl shadow-blue-950/50"
      >
        <div class="text-lg self-center">
          <a
            href="https://github.com/TriFullKim"
            class="text-3xl font-extrabold underline underline-offset-3 decoration-sky-400 content-center hover:text-sky-500"
            >@TriFullKim</a
          >
          <p>
            반갑습니다!! 현재 학부연구생으로 <u>인공지능을 연구</u> 하고 있으며,
            <strong> 서비스 출시(앱개발)에 관심 </strong>을 두고 공부 중 입니다.
            디자인에도 관심을 갖고 있으며, 동아리/연구실 <strong>로고</strong>를
            Adobe Illustrator와 같은 디자인 툴을 사용하여
            <strong>제작</strong>한 경험이 있습니다.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <a
            href="mailto:mail@trifull.kim"
            class="font-mono badge badge-neutral">mail@trifull.kim</a
          >
          <a href="https://www.pnu-cvsp.com/" class="font-mono badge badge-info"
            >CVSP Lab.</a
          >
          <a
            href="https://github.com/TriFullKim"
            class="font-mono badge badge-info">Github</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </h1>
    <div class="h-3"></div>
    <Section title="Education">
      <ul class="list-disc px-8">
        <li>B.S. in Electrical Engineering , PKNU, Feb. 2021 – present.</li>
      </ul>
    </Section>
    <Section title="Publication">
      <Publication />
    </Section>
    <div class="h-3"></div>
    <Section title="Design">
      <Design />
    </Section>
  </main>
  <div class="h-24"></div>
</Layout>
